import React from "react";
import ReactDOM from "react-dom";
import DnD from "./components/dragAndDrop";
import "bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css";
import Container from "react-bootstrap/Container";
import Row from "react-bootstrap/Row";
import Col from "react-bootstrap/Col";
import Form from "react-bootstrap/Form";

ReactDOM.render(
  <Container fluid>
    <Form>
      <Row>
        <Col>Anomaly Detection Server</Col>
      </Row>
      <Row>
        <Col xs="auto">
          <Form.Group>
            <Form.Label>Choose Algo</Form.Label>
            <Form.Control as="select" className="mr-sm-2">
              <option value="1">Regression</option>
              <option value="2">Hybrid</option>
            </Form.Control>
          </Form.Group>
        </Col>
        <Col>
          <Form.File
            id="custom-file-translate-scss"
            label="Custom file input"
            lang="en"
            custom
          >
            <Form.File.Input isValid />
            <Form.File.Label data-browse="Button text">
              Upload Learn CSV file
            </Form.File.Label>
            <Form.Control.Feedback type="valid">
              You did it!
            </Form.Control.Feedback>
          </Form.File>
        </Col>
        <Col>
          <Form.File
            id="custom-file-translate-scss"
            label="Custom file input"
            lang="en"
            custom
          >
            <Form.File.Input isValid />
            <Form.File.Label data-browse="Button text">
              Upload Anomaly CSV file
            </Form.File.Label>
            <Form.Control.Feedback type="valid">
              You did it!
            </Form.Control.Feedback>
          </Form.File>
        </Col>
      </Row>
    </Form>
  </Container>,
  document.getElementById("root")
);
